text: This cosy place has a decent friendly singing community. Quite nice to hang out over beers & songs. Also a good place as last destination when hopping; they close relatively late.
Good service and the waitress here are friendly

Very nice place, waitress here is very friendly and warm, enjoyed karaoke singing here, prices are reasonable.

Drinks' prices are very reasonable, service staff friendly and warm. Enjoyed the playing pool, karaoke singing, card games and dice games. The people who go to this pub are really friendly and most of them have patronized for between 1 to 9 years.
